etomica.data.meter

Class MeterPressureByVolumeChange

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.data.meter.MeterPressureByVolumeChange
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDataSource, IEtomicaDataSource, java.io.Serializable

    public class MeterPressureByVolumeChange
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEtomicaDataSource, java.io.Serializable
    Evaluates the pressure by examining the change in energy accompanying small changes in volume. Pressure is approximately log()/deltaV where x is one of the values returned by getData ( is that value averaged) and deltaV is the change in volume associated with that x value. deltaV = s * V where s is the scaling factor (available via getScalingDataSource)
